3300.name: Talisman of Kadesh
3300.description: A strange talisman obtained after slaying Kadesh. Take this to Sagittarius Hamil of the Village of Floran.

3301.name: Talisman of Snake
3301.description: Talisman that is related to a serpent totem spirit worshipped by Breka orcs. Take it to Prefect Vokian of Town of Giran.

3302.name: Mithril Clip
3302.description: A key ingredient in restoring the Crescent Bow. Take this, along with the rest of the ingredients, to Magister Gauen of the Ivory Tower.

3303.name: Stakato Chitin
3303.description: A key ingredient in restoring the Crescent Bow. Take this, along with the rest of the ingredients, to Magister Gauen of the Ivory Tower.

3304.name: Reinforced Bowstring
3304.description: A key ingredient in restoring the Crescent Bow. Take this, along with the rest of the ingredients, to Magister Gauen of the Ivory Tower.

3305.name: Manashen's Horn
3305.description: A key ingredient in restoring the Crescent Bow. Take this, along with the rest of the ingredients, to Magister Gauen of the Ivory Tower.

3306.name: Blood of Lizardman
3306.description: The blood shed by Leto Lizardmen. Kadesh appears when enough of this is gathered.

3307.name: Mark of Witchcraft
3307.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Test of Witchcraft. An occupation change related item.

3308.name: Orim's Diagram
3308.description: A diagram of relics, given by Orim of the Shadow. The 6 jewels needed for opening the Cube of Aklantoth are depicted here.

3309.name: Alexandria's Book
3309.description: A book that contains records on who purchased Aklantoth's Gems. "Magister Iker, Magister Kaira, Trader Lara"

3310.name: Iker's List
3310.description: Collect and bring back 20 dire Wyrm fangs, 20 Leto lizardman charms, and 20 enchanted stone golem heartstones.

3311.name: Dire Wyrm Fang
3311.description: The fangs of a slain Dire Wyrm. Collect 20 of these and take them to Magister Iker.

3312.name: Leto Lizardman Charm
3312.description: A totem obtained after slaying the Leto Lizardman. Collect 20 of these and take them to Magister Iker.

3313.name: Enchanted Stone Golem Heartstone
3313.description: A crystal found amongst the shattered fragments of an enchanted stone golem. Collect 20 of these and take them to Magister Iker.

3314.name: Lara's Memo
3314.description: Trader Lara's sales records. It is recorded that a man named Ismel bought the jewel from Lara.

3315.name: Nestle's Memo
3315.description: Trader Lara's purchase records. It is recorded that Leopold of the Black Lion brought the jewel.

3316.name: Leopold's Journal
3316.description: A portion of Leopold's Diary. It is recorded that 3 deserters died and became undead while escaping to the Wastelands.

3317.name: Aklantoth 1st Gem
3317.description: Gem that can be obtained from Magister Iker. Find all 6 of Aklantoth gems and take them to Orim the Shadow.

3318.name: Aklantoth 2nd Gem
3318.description: The gem given by Magister Kaira. Find all 6 of Aklantoth gems and take them to Orim the Shadow.

3319.name: Aklantoth 3rd Gem
3319.description: The gem that can be obtained by killing a nameless revenant. Find all 6 of Aklantoth gems and take them to Orim the Shadow.

3320.name: Aklantoth 4th Gem
3320.description: The gem that can be obtained by slaying a skeletal mercenary. Find all 6 of Aklantoth gems and take them to Orim the Shadow.

3321.name: Aklantoth 5th Gem
3321.description: The gem that can be obtained by slaying a skeletal mercenary. Find all 6 of Aklantoth gems and take them to Orim the Shadow.

3322.name: Aklantoth 6th Gem
3322.description: The gem that can be obtained by slaying a skeletal mercenary. Find all 6 of Aklantoth gems and take them to Orim the Shadow.

3323.name: 1st Brimstone
3323.description: A mark left behind by the Drevanul Prince Zeruel when escaping from his binds.

3324.name: Orim's Instructions
3324.description: A set of instructions written by Orim of the Shadow. The instructions are to bring back the Sword of Binding and Soul Trap Crystal.

3325.name: Orim's 1st Letter
3325.description: A letter from Orim of the Shadow to Sir Karol Vasper of the Town of Gludin. The letter asks for the loan of the Sword of the Seal.

3326.name: Orim's 2nd Letter
3326.description: A letter from Orim of the Shadows to Magister Iker of Town of Giran. The letter asks for the loan of the Soul-trap Crystal.

3327.name: Sir Vasper's Letter
3327.description: A letter from Sir Klaus Vasper to Vadin of the Town of Oren. The letter gives permission for the use of the Sword of Binding.

3328.name: Vadin's Crucifix
3328.description: A holy crucifix of the order, given by Vadin. Take this and go hunt Tamlin Orcs.

3329.name: Tamlin Orc Amulet
3329.description: Amulets that the Tamlin Orcs carry for sorcery purposes. Gather 20 of these and take them to Vadin.

3330.name: Vadin's Sanctions
3330.description: A sanctions letter from Vadin allowing for the use of the Sword of Binding. Take this to Sir Klaus Vasper of the Town of Gludin.

3331.name: Iker's Amulet
3331.description: An amulet given by Magister Iker. It is said to have powers of protection against evil...

3332.name: Soultrap Crystal
3332.description: A crystal with the power to trap and seal the soul of a monster. Use this to seal the spirit of the Drevanul Zeruel.

3333.name: Purgatory Key
3333.description: A key needed to close Aklantoth's Chest. Take this to Orim of the Shadow.

3334.name: Zeruel Bind Crystal
3334.description: A crystal that contains the trapped soul of the Drevanul Zeruel. Take this to Orim of the Shadow.

3335.name: 2nd Brimstone
3335.description: A mark left behind by the Drevanul Prince Zeruel while escaping from the body of Fisher Evert.

3336.name: Mark of Summoner
3336.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Test of the Summoner. An occupation change related item.

3337.name: Leto Lizardman Amulet
3337.description: An amulet obtained after slaying a Leto Lizardman. Gather 30 of these and take them back to Trader Lara.

3338.name: Sac of Redspores
3338.description: Red spores obtained from the bodies of the giant fungus. Gather 30 of these and take them back to Trader Lara.

3339.name: Karul Bugbear Totem
3339.description: A totem obtained after slaying the Karul Bugbear. Gather 30 of these and take them back to Trader Lara.

3340.name: Shards of Manashen
3340.description: A shard of the shattered Manashen. Gather 30 of these and take them back to Trader Lara.

3341.name: Breka Orc Totem
3341.description: A totem that can be obtained after slaying a Breka orc. Collect 30 of them and take them to Trader Lara.

3342.name: Crimson Bloodstone
3342.description: A spirit stone embedded in the body of a fettered soul. Gather 30 of these and take them back to Trader Lara.

3343.name: Talons of Tyrant
3343.description: The talon of a slain tyrant. Gather 30 of these and take them back to Trader Lara.

3344.name: Wings of Droneant
3344.description: Wings obtained after slaying Noble Ants at the Ant's Nest. Gather 30 of these and take them back to Trader Lara.

3345.name: Tusk of Windsus
3345.description: The tusks of a slain Windsus. Gather 30 of these and take them back to Trader Lara.

3346.name: Fangs of Wyrm
3346.description: The fangs of a slain Wyrm. Gather 30 of these and take them back to Trader Lara.

3347.name: Lara's 1st List
3347.description: Collect 30 Leto lizardman amulets from the Plains of the Lizardmen and 30 units of red spore dust from the giant fungus in the Sea of Spores.

3348.name: Lara's 2nd List
3348.description: Collect 30 Karul bugbear totems from Hunters Valley and 30 shards of manashen from the Crater of the Ivory Tower.

3349.name: Lara's 3rd List
3349.description: Collect 30 Breka orc totems from Breka's Stronghold and 30 crimson bloodstones of fettered soul from Death Pass.

3350.name: Lara's 4th List
3350.description: Collect 30 Tyrant Talons from the Wastelands and 30 Windsus Tusks from Death Pass.

3351.name: Lara's 5th List
3351.description: Collect 30 noble ant wings from the Ant Nest and 30 Wyrm fangs from Gorgon's Flower Garden.

3352.name: Galatea's Letter
3352.description: A letter from Head Summoner Galatea to Trader Lara in the Town of Dion.

3353.name: Beginner's Arcana
3353.description: An Arcana card used by apprentice Summoners. You must have this in order to participate in Summoner battles.

3354.name: Almors's Arcana
3354.description: Summoner Almors's Arcana. The proof of victory from a battle. Take this to Head Summoner Galatea.

3355.name: Camoniell's Arcana
3355.description: Summoner Camoniell's. The proof of victory from a battle. Take this to Head Summoner Galatea.

3356.name: Belthus's Arcana
3356.description: Summoner Belthus's Arcana. The proof of victory from a battle. Take this to Head Summoner Galatea.

3357.name: Basillia's Arcana
3357.description: Summoner Basillia's Arcana. The proof of victory from a battle. Take this to Head Summoner Galatea.

3358.name: Celestiel's Arcana
3358.description: Summoner Celestiel's Arcana. The proof of victory from a battle. Take this to Head Summoner Galatea.

3359.name: Brynthea's Arcana
3359.description: Summoner Brynthea's Arcana. The proof of victory from a battle. Take this to Head Summoner Galatea.

3360.name: 1st Crystal of Starting
3360.description: An indication that a Summoner battle has begun.

3361.name: 1st Crystal of Inprogress
3361.description: An indication that a Summoner battle is in progress.

3362.name: 1st Crystal of Foul
3362.description: An indication that foul play was involved in a Summoner battle. Take this to Summoner Almors.

3363.name: 1st Crystal of Defeat
3363.description: An indication that the Summoner has been defeated in battle. Take this to Summoner Almors.

3364.name: 1st Crystal of Victory
3364.description: An indication that the Summoner has been victorious in a battle. Take this to Summoner Almors.

3365.name: 2nd Crystal of Starting
3365.description: An indication that a Summoner battle has begun.

3366.name: 2nd Crystal of Inprogress
3366.description: An indication that a Summoner battle is in progress.

3367.name: 2nd Crystal of Foul
3367.description: An indication that foul play was involved in a Summoner battle. Take this to Summoner Camoniell.

3368.name: 2nd Crystal of Defeat
3368.description: An indication that the Summoner has been defeated in a battle. Take this to Summoner Camoniell.

3369.name: 2nd Crystal of Victory
3369.description: An indication that the Summoner has been victorious in a battle. Take this to Summoner Camoniell.

3370.name: 3rd Crystal of Starting
3370.description: An indication that a Summoner battle has begun.

3371.name: 3rd Crystal of Inprogress
3371.description: An indication that a Summoner battle is in progress.

3372.name: 3rd Crystal of Foul
3372.description: An indication that foul play was involved in a summoner battle. Take this to Summoner Belthus.

3373.name: 3rd Crystal of Defeat
3373.description: An indication that the Summoner has been defeated in a battle. Take this to Summoner Belthus.

3374.name: 3rd Crystal of Victory
3374.description: An indication that the Summoner has been victorious in a battle. Take this to Summoner Belthus.

3375.name: 4th Crystal of Starting
3375.description: An indication that a Summoner battle has begun.

3376.name: 4th Crystal of Inprogress
3376.description: An indication that a Summoner battle is in progress.

3377.name: 4th Crystal of Foul
3377.description: An indication that foul play was involved in a Summoner battle. Take this to Summoner Basillia.

3378.name: 4th Crystal of Defeat
3378.description: An indication that the Summoner has been defeated in a battle. Take this to Summoner Basillia.

3379.name: 4th Crystal of Victory
3379.description: An indication that the Summoner has been victorious in a battle. Take this to Summoner Basillia.

3380.name: 5th Crystal of Starting
3380.description: An indication that a Summoner battle has begun.

3381.name: 5th Crystal of Inprogress
3381.description: An indication that a Summoner battle is in progress.

3382.name: 5th Crystal of Foul
3382.description: An indication that foul play was involved in a Summoner battle. Take this to Summoner Celestiel.

3383.name: 5th Crystal of Defeat
3383.description: An indication that the Summoner has been defeated in a battle. Take this to Summoner Celestiel.

3384.name: 5th Crystal of Victory
3384.description: An indication that the Summoner has been victorious in a battle. Take this to Summoner Celestiel.

3385.name: 6th Crystal of Starting
3385.description: An indication that a Summoner battle has begun.

3386.name: 6th Crystal of Inprogress
3386.description: An indication that a Summoner battle is in progress.

3387.name: 6th Crystal of Foul
3387.description: An indication that foul play was involved in a Summoner battle. Take this to Summoner Brynthea.

3388.name: 6th Crystal of Defeat
3388.description: An indication that the Summoner has been defeated in a Summoner battle. Take this to Summoner Brynthea.

3389.name: 6th Crystal of Victory
3389.description: An indication that the Summoner has been victorious in a Summoner battle. Take this to Summoner Brynthea.

3390.name: Mark of Lord
3390.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Test of the Lord. An item for occupational change.

3391.name: Ordeal Necklace
3391.description: A necklace given to those who are attempting the Test of the Lord. Go seek 5 Chiefs of different tribes and return with their approvals.

3392.name: Varkee's Charm
3392.description: The Atuba chief Varkee's charm. Go back to him after completing this task.

3393.name: Tantus's Charm
3393.description: The Neruga chief Tantus's charm. Go back to him after completing this task.

3394.name: Hatos's Charm
3394.description: The Urutu Chief Hatos's charm. Go back to him after completing this task.

3395.name: Takuna's Charm
3395.description: The Duda-Mara Chief Takuna's charm. Go back to him after completing this task.

3396.name: Chianta's Charm
3396.description: Gandi Chief Chianta's charm. Go back to him after completing this task.

3397.name: Manakia's Orders
3397.description: A document containing Seer Manakia's orders. It tells you to kill Breka orc shamans and Breka orc overlords and bring back 20 Breka orc fangs.

3398.name: Breka Orc Fang
3398.description: A Breka orc's fang. Collect 20 of them and take them to Seer Manakia.

3399.name: Manakia's Amulet
3399.description: A mark received after passing Manakia's test. Take this to Atuba Chief Varkees.
